extends layout.pug

block content 
  article.grid-container.portfolio-intro
    div
      h1 Featured Work
      p.lead.text-light
        | Here's some of my recent development work, featuring applications of JavaScript and related technologies. (This portfolio site was itself built with Express on Node.js.)
  article.grid-container.portfolio-index
    
    .grid-x.grid-margin-x.small-up-2.medium-up-2.large-up-3

      each project in projects
        .cell
          a(href=`/project/${project.id}`)
            img.thumbnail(src=project.image_urls[0])
            h5= project_name
